snippet.title: Playable Music : mapping ADSR to block parameters
snippet.description:
Wishlist on Steam!
https://store.steampowered.com/app/737100/Squarewave_Maker/

Official Discord server : https://discordapp.com/invite/squarewavemaker

Connection of ADSR to height offset and to emissive gain in Squarewave Maker.

Squarewave Maker is a sandbox rhythm action game where the level is your musical instrument.

Website: http://www.squarewavemaker.com
Twitter: http://www.twitter.com/SquarewaveMaker
Facebook: http://www.facebook.com/SquarewaveMaker/
